results.title: Asheville Concierge Medicine - Dr. Smith
results.content: Dr. Jane Smith offers personalized concierge medicine in Asheville, NC. Membership includes unlimited visits, same-day appointments, and 24/7 access. Monthly fee: $200-300.

results.title: Mountain Direct Primary Care
results.content: Direct primary care practice accepting new patients. No insurance billing, flat monthly fee of $150 for adults. Located downtown Asheville.

results.title: WNC Health Partners - Concierge Services
results.content: Full-service concierge medical practice. Annual membership starts at $2500. Includes comprehensive annual physical, unlimited office visits, and care coordination.
